  "detailed_description": "<strong>Puzzlerio</strong> is a <strong>minimalist</strong> and <strong>relaxing</strong> experience where you will create a factory that takes ores from <strong>one point to another</strong>. <strong>Refine ores</strong> to turn them into bar ores, use different resources to transport the ores and do everything necessary to <strong>complete the factory</strong>.<br><br><strong>Transport ores with the Transport Belt</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2633630/extras/df2f5bac14eff8edb0d38e69939d25f2.poster.avif?t=1729198676\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2633630/extras/df2f5bac14eff8edb0d38e69939d25f2.webm?t=1729198676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2633630/extras/df2f5bac14eff8edb0d38e69939d25f2.mp4?t=1729198676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Refine ores with the Furnace</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2633630/extras/51c88cdd3b85f886b988bd986eab5442.poster.avif?t=1729198676\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2633630/extras/51c88cdd3b85f886b988bd986eab5442.webm?t=1729198676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2633630/extras/51c88cdd3b85f886b988bd986eab5442.mp4?t=1729198676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Take ores from one transport belt to another with the <i>Inserter</i></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/